{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"16bf4c7c-8ebd-4997-b54e-69f2c80466ff","content":"","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01GJJApwmRiFTfgFuioASFqF","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Creating runsettings migration"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_017bXCgAbT3m9VnGrZSgDyoA","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-93c39e612491464189b6d4166ba9f778/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <!-- Replaces the TestTimeout property from .testsettings (value in ms) -->\n    <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n    <!-- Replaces AssemblyResolution / deployment settings -->\n    <DeploymentEnabled>true</DeploymentEnabled>\n  </MSTest>\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <!-- Replaces the CodeCoverage DataCollector from .testsettings -->\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n                     uri=\"datacollector://Microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n                     assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector.SingleFileCodeCoverageDataCollector, Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b03f5f7f11d50a3a\">\n      </DataCollector>\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-93c39e612491464189b6d4166ba9f778/local.runsettings."},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01CkCDSaEm9U3KCREH7GsDwS","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-93c39e612491464189b6d4166ba9f778/TestProject.csproj","old_str":"  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n  </PropertyGroup>","new_str":"  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n    <RunSettingsFilePath>$(MSBuildProjectDirectory)\\local.runsettings</RunSettingsFilePath>\n  </PropertyGroup>"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-93c39e612491464189b6d4166ba9f778/TestProject.csproj."}],"interactionId":"6b4f008a-876a-4f24-bbce-e45c3bec2c94","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has a `.testsettings` file with:\n1. Assembly resolution / test deployment settings\n2. A test timeout of 30000ms (30 seconds)\n3. A code coverage data collector\n\nThey need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file, which is the modern replacement for `.testsettings`. Let me create a `.runsettings` file and update the `.csproj` to reference it.\n\nThe `.testsettings` format is legacy and no longer supported by modern MSTest. The migration path is:\n\n1. **TestTimeout** → `<MSTest><TestTimeout>` or `[Timeout]` attribute, or in `.runsettings` under `<MSTest>` section\n\n\n2. **Code Coverage** → `<DataCollectors>` in `.runsettings`\n3. **Assembly resolution / deployment** → `<MSTest><DeploymentEnabled>` in `.runsettings`\n\nNow I'll build the `.runsettings` file with these settings mapped over.","outputTokens":830,"requestId":"7C34:57F7E:2AD7674:2FC937F:69F95990"},"id":"656fdef4-1652-43f5-bc25-54747979503f","timestamp":"2026-05-05T02:44:44.236Z","parentId":"af8e31a7-791c-4851-bf29-4919c53e8a3e"}
